"...\n"
"4 equals 2 * 2\n"
"6 equals 2 * 3\n"
"8 equals 2 * 4\n"
"9 equals 3 * 3"

#: ../../tutorial/controlflow.rst:180
msgid ""
"The :keyword:`continue` statement continues with the next iteration of the "
"loop::"
